s=\"font_0\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>National Water Resources Management Agency</strong>&#8211; Sierra Leone</h4>\n</div></div><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div id=\"i6bh2cee_0\" class=\"txtNew\" data-packed=\"true\">\n<h5 class=\"font_5\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Little</strong> About Us</h5>\n</div>\n</div></div><div class=\"w-separator size_small\"></div><div class=\"w-image style_shadow-1 align_center animate_afc\"><div class=\"w-image-h\"><img width=\"550\" height=\"130\" src=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/nw.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" srcset=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/nw.png 550w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/nw-300x71.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></div></div><div id=\"ultimate-heading-53716a0792d90a5a4\" class=\"uvc-heading ult-adjust-bottom-margin ultimate-heading-53716a0792d90a5a4 uvc-7270 \" data-hspacer=\"no_spacer\"  data-halign=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><div class=\"uvc-heading-spacer no_spacer\" style=\"top\"></div><div class=\"uvc-sub-heading ult-responsive\"  data-ultimate-target='.uvc-heading.ultimate-heading-53716a0792d90a5a4 .uvc-sub-heading '  data-responsive-json-new='{\"font-size\":\"\",\"line-height\":\"\"}'  style=\"font-weight:normal;margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:20px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The National Water Resources Management Agency (NWRMA) was established by an Act of parliament in 2017, to protect, manage and regulate surface and ground water resources in Sierra Leone with an overall vision of becoming one of the leading water resources management Agencies in West Africa. The Agency is responsible for granting of water rights, water resources allotment among competing users, formulation of regulatory measures, information/data collection and sharing on water resources, with a view also to controlling pollution. Trans-boundary water resource issues also fall under the mandate of the Agency.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">As the country’s only water resources management entity, raising public awareness is key for its operation as this will serve as a platform to interface with raw water users and key stakeholders in the management of water resources in Sierra Leone.</p>\n</div></div><div class=\"w-btn-wrapper width_auto align_center\"><a class=\"w-btn us-btn-style_4\" href=\"/about/\"><span class=\"w-btn-label\">Read More&#8230;</span></a></div></div></div></div><div class=\"vc_col-sm-2 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><!-- Row Backgrounds --><div class=\"upb_color\" data-bg-override=\"0\" data-bg-color=\"rgba(224,224,224,0.7)\" data-fadeout=\"\" data-fadeout-percentage=\"30\" data-parallax-content=\"\" data-parallax-content-sense=\"30\" data-row-effect-mobile-disable=\"true\" data-img-parallax-mobile-disable=\"true\" data-rtl=\"false\"  data-custom-vc-row=\"\"  data-vc=\"6.1\"  data-is_old_vc=\"\"  data-theme-support=\"\"   data-overlay=\"false\" data-overlay-color=\"\" data-overlay-pattern=\"\" data-overlay-pattern-opacity=\"\" data-overlay-pattern-size=\"\"    ></div><section class=\"l-section wpb_row height_medium\"><div class=\"l-section-h i-cf\"><div class=\"g-cols vc_row type_default valign_top\"><div class=\"vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h2 class=\"fancy-heading themify-text-center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"sub-head\">What We Do</span></h2>\n</div></div><div class=\"w-separator size_small\"></div><div class=\"g-cols wpb_row  type_default valign_top vc_inner\"><div class=\"vc_col-sm-3 wpb_column vc_column_container animate_afb\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"w-image align_center\"><div class=\"w-image-h\"><img class=\"g-placeholder\" src=\"/assets/plugins/us-core/assets/images/placeholder.svg\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" alt=\"\"></div></div><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h6 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>REGULATION</strong></h6>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Water Resources Authority (NWRMA) sustainably and equitably allocates water resources among the various competing needs. NWRMA also requires that stakeholders are involved in the process. The “Water use Permit” is used to carry out this function.</p>\n</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"vc_col-sm-3 wpb_column vc_column_container animate_afb\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"w-image align_center\"><div class=\"w-image-h\"><img width=\"225\" height=\"225\" src=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2021/03/WRP.png\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2021/03/WRP.png 225w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2021/03/WRP-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" /></div></div><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h6 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>PROTECTION</strong></h6>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The National Water Resources Management Agency (NWRMA) also controls pollution and improves water quality in the country’s water bodies. This involves regular water quality tests and integrating land use activities into NWRMA Water Quality Control programs.</p>\n</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"vc_col-sm-3 wpb_column vc_column_container animate_afb\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"w-image align_center\"><div class=\"w-image-h\"><img width=\"225\" height=\"225\" src=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2021/03/Download.png\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2021/03/Download.png 225w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2021/03/Download-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" /></div></div><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h6 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>PUBLIC INFORMATION</strong></h6>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The Agency collects all information on water resources, analyses, stores and disseminates it. This information is critical for water allocation, water resources investment decision making and modeling to enact scenarios to better understand the impact of climate change in future.</p>\n</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"vc_col-sm-3 wpb_column vc_column_container animate_afb\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"w-image align_center\"><div class=\"w-image-h\"><img width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2021/03/CCA.png\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2021/03/CCA.png 200w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2021/03/CCA-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" /></div></div><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h6 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>CLIMATE CHANGE ADAPTATION</strong></h6>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The Authority undertakes climate actions in terms of mitigation and adaptation to minimizing the effects of global warming and climate change.</p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"l-section wpb_row height_small color_primary with_img parallax_fixed with_overlay with_shape\"><div class=\"l-section-img\" style=\"background-image: url(https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/bg-1.jpg);background-repeat: no-repeat;\" data-img-width=\"1199\" data-img-height=\"800\"></div><div class=\"l-section-overlay\" style=\"background: rgba(32,133,111,0.73)\"></div><div class=\"l-section-shape type_wave pos_bottom\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 4 64 4\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\">\n\n\t<path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M64 6 C32 0 32 12 0 6 L0 8 L64 8 Z\"/>\n\n</svg></div><div class=\"l-section-h i-cf\"><div class=\"g-cols vc_row type_boxes valign_top\"><div class=\"vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Online</strong> Resources</h5>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The National Water Resources Management Agency website contains an increasing number of resources that we are making widley available on the site. At present we have a wide range of data, national and river basin specific maps and publications.</p>\n</div></div><div class=\"w-separator size_medium\"></div><div class=\"g-cols wpb_row  type_boxes valign_top vc_inner\"><div class=\"vc_col-sm-4 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"ult-just-icon-wrapper  \"><div class=\"align-icon\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<a class=\"aio-tooltip 6a0792d9119ae\" href=\"https://www.nwrma.com/data/\"  data-toggle=\"tooltip\" data-placement=\"\"><div class=\"aio-icon none \"  style=\"color:#eeee22;font-size:99px;display:inline-block;\">\n\t<i class=\"Defaults-adjust\"></i>\n</div></a></div></div><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"/data/\"><strong>Data</strong></a></h5>\n</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"vc_col-sm-4 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"ult-just-icon-wrapper  \"><div class=\"align-icon\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<a class=\"aio-tooltip 6a0792d911d6f\" href=\"https://www.nwrma.com/maps/\" title=\"Maps\"  data-toggle=