</div><div class=\"w-vwrapper usg_vwrapper_1 align_left valign_top \"><h2 class=\"w-post-elm post_title usg_post_title_1 entry-title color_link_inherit\"><a href=\"/parliament-approves-the-new-director-general-for-nwrma/\">Parliament Approves the New Director General for NWRMA</a></h2><div class=\"w-hwrapper usg_hwrapper_1 align_left valign_top wrap \"><time class=\"w-post-elm post_date usg_post_date_1 entry-date published\" datetime=\"2025-11-11T02:00:34+00:00\" title=\"11 November 2025 at 02:00:34 +00:00\">11 Nov 2025</time><div class=\"w-post-elm post_comments usg_post_comments_1 layout_amount color_link_inherit\"><i class=\"far fa-comments\"></i><a class=\"smooth-scroll\" href=\"/parliament-approves-the-new-director-general-for-nwrma/#respond\">0</a></div></div><div class=\"w-post-elm post_content usg_post_content_1\">The new Director General, Ing. Pierre Palmer has been approved by Parliament as the successor to the outgoing Director General,&hellip;</div></div>\t</div>\n\n</article>\n\n<article class=\"w-grid-item size_1x1 post-8626 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-news\" data-id=\"8626\">\n\n\t<div class=\"w-grid-item-h\">\n\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"w-post-elm post_image usg_post_image_1 stretched\"><a href=\"/iwmi-concludes-scoping-mission-to-sierra-leone/\" aria-label=\"IWMI Concludes Scoping Mission to Sierra Leone\"><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2025/06/IMG_3920-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2025/06/IMG_3920-150x150.jpg 150w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2025/06/IMG_3920-600x600.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a></div><div class=\"w-post-elm post_taxonomy usg_post_taxonomy_1 style_badge color_link_inherit\"><a class=\"w-btn us-btn-style_badge\" href=\"/category/news/\">News</a></div><div class=\"w-vwrapper usg_vwrapper_1 align_left valign_top \"><h2 class=\"w-post-elm post_title usg_post_title_1 entry-title color_link_inherit\"><a href=\"/iwmi-concludes-scoping-mission-to-sierra-leone/\">IWMI Concludes Scoping Mission to Sierra Leone</a></h2><div class=\"w-hwrapper usg_hwrapper_1 align_left valign_top wrap \"><time class=\"w-post-elm post_date usg_post_date_1 entry-date published\" datetime=\"2025-06-10T18:29:51+00:00\" title=\"10 June 2025 at 18:29:51 +00:00\">10 Jun 2025</time><div class=\"w-post-elm post_comments usg_post_comments_1 layout_amount color_link_inherit\"><i class=\"far fa-comments\"></i><a class=\"smooth-scroll\" href=\"/iwmi-concludes-scoping-mission-to-sierra-leone/#respond\">0</a></div></div><div class=\"w-post-elm post_content usg_post_content_1\">Freetown, Sierra Leone –June 10, 2025 – A high-level scoping mission from the International Water Management Institute (IWMI) has concluded&hellip;</div></div>\t</div>\n\n</article>\n\n</div>\t<div class=\"w-grid-json hidden\" onclick='return {&quot;ajax_url&quot;:&quot;https:\\/\\/nwrma.gov.sl\\/wp-admin\\/admin-ajax.php&quot;,&quot;permalink_url&quot;:&quot;https:\\/\\/nwrma.gov.sl\\/iwmi-concludes-scoping-mission-to-sierra-leone\\/&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:&quot;us_ajax_grid&quot;,&quot;max_num_pages&quot;:11,&quot;infinite_scroll&quot;:0,&quot;template_vars&quot;:{&quot;query_args&quot;:{&quot;post_type&quot;:[&quot;post&quot;],&quot;post_status&quot;:[&quot;publish&quot;],&quot;post__not_in&quot;:[7434],&quot;orderby&quot;:{&quot;date&quot;:&quot;DESC&quot;},&quot;posts_per_page&quot;:&quot;4&quot;},&quot;post_id&quot;:7434,&quot;us_grid_index&quot;:1,&quot;us_grid_ajax_index&quot;:1,&quot;exclude_items&quot;:&quot;none&quot;,&quot;items_offset&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;items_layout&quot;:&quot;blog_cards&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;grid&quot;,&quot;columns&quot;:&quot;4&quot;,&quot;img_size&quot;:&quot;thumbnail&quot;,&quot;overriding_link&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}}'></div>\n\n</div><div class=\"w-btn-wrapper 